Milo's Triad of Terror map pack.4: trust me when i say READ ME.txt

_sName: Milo's Triad of Terror Map Pack
_sText:
Milo's Triad of Terror map pack is a map pack consisting of three maps. de_clay, de_boneyard, and de_maizefarm are the maps included. At first, these maps were just for me and my friends to mess around on. However, a little after I created de_boneyard I thought of creating a map pack to publish online. These secret filled maps are great to play casually, and are designed with fun in mind.

de_clay is a swamp dominated by darkness, and requires a flashlight or night vision goggles to know where you're going.

de_boneyard is a graveyard consisting of pumpkins, walls, and (obviously) graves! Be warned however, sometimes the dark and ghoulish night fog reddens, and a clutter of skeletons arrive to dance!

de_maizefarm is in the frontlines of a human vs. alien war. Taking place on a rinky-dink farm with plenty of corn to go around!

Feel free to host this on your server!

(remember theres like easter eggs everywhere so try and find them all!)
